{
  "resources": {
    "tag:me@example.com,2016:widgets": {
      "href": "/widgets/"
    },
    "tag:me@example.com,2016:widget": {
      "href-template": "/widgets/{widget_id}",
      "href-vars": {
        "widget_id": "http://example.org/param/widget"
      },
      "hints": {
        "allow": ["GET", "PUT", "DELETE", "PATCH"],
        "formats": {
          "application/json": {}
        },
        "accept-patch": ["application/json-patch+json"],
        "accept-post": ["application/xml"],
        "accept-ranges": ["bytes"]
      }
    }
  }
}

section.t:
Templated links are indicated with an “href-template” property, whose value is a URI Template
. When “href-template” is present, the Resource Object MUST have a “href-vars” property;
see “Resolving Templated Links”.

